not infrequent case where MCSCF wave functions are not attainable for higher roots
of a given symmetry. (b) The dependence of extended CI wave functions on the
choice of SA-MCSCF orbitals is considered and this property is used to provide
an internal estimate of the reliability of interstate matrix elements. (c) Transition
dipole matrix elements between the llZ+ and Z12+ states in MgO are determined.
